INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("482", "1", "2019-01-04 22:23:17", "2019-01-04 22:23:17", "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dont get hung up on things that dont fucking work. Never, never assume that what you have achieved is fucking good enough. Dont fucking lie to yourself. Design as if your fucking life depended on it. Respect your fucking craft. Someday is not a fucking day of the week. Design as if your fucking life depended on it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Respect your fucking craft. A good fucking composition is the result of a hierarchy consisting of clearly contrasting elements set with distinct alignments containing irregular intervals of negative space. Dont worry about what other people fucking think. Dont fucking lie to yourself. Think about all the fucking possibilities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Design as if your fucking life depended on it. Design is all about fucking relationshipsthe relationship of form and content, the relationship of elements, the relationship of designer and user. Never let your guard down by thinking youre fucking good enough. When you sit down to work, external critics arent the enemy. Its you who you must to fight against to do great fucking work. You must overcome yourself. Someday is not a fucking day of the week. Nothing of value comes to you without fucking working at it. Think about all the fucking possibilities. Sometimes it is appropriate to place various typographic elements on the outside of the fucking left margin of text to maintain a strong vertical axis. This practice is referred to as exdenting and is most often used with bullets and quotations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Never let your guard down by thinking youre fucking good enough. Dont fucking lie to yourself. Dont fucking lie to yourself. Someday is not a fucking day of the week. Dont worry about what other people fucking think. The graphic designers first fucking consideration is always the size and shape of the format, whether for the printed page or for digital display. Dont worry about what other people fucking think.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Creativity is a fucking work-ethic. Learn from fucking criticism. Respect your fucking craft. Practice wont get you anywhere if you mindlessly fucking practice the same thing. Change only occurs when you work deliberately with purpose toward a goal. Never, never assume that what you have achieved is fucking good enough. To go partway is easy, but mastering anything requires hard fucking work. Widows and orphans are terrible fucking tragedies, both in real life and definitely in typography.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->", "Lorem Fucking Ipsum", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "481-revision-v1", "", "", "2019-01-04 22:23:17", "2019-01-04 22:23:17", "", "481", "http://localhost/equius/481-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
